ttp://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Ten gale Leo, teigiantis, kad su Diddy nuo t≈≥ laik≈≥ nebebendravo </figcaption></figure></div><p>Combsas taip pat yra nuo seno pagarsƒójƒôs jaun≈≥ talent≈≥ ‚Äûglobƒójas‚Äú. Jo prote≈æƒó Usheris pasakoja paauglystƒóje beveik metus gyvenƒôs su Diddy/Daddy, kur ‚Äûmatƒó dalyk≈≥‚Äú ir buvo supa≈æindintas su sekso ƒØvairove. Taip pat su Diddy laikƒÖ leido ma≈æutis Bieberis, kuriam ≈°itas dƒódƒó <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kxHwfTpQjpc&amp;ab_channel=JustinBieber">dovanojo ma≈°inƒÖ</a> ir ≈æadƒójo namƒÖ. Tiesa, per tiktokus dabar persiritusi neva niekur neskelbta Bieberio daina su ≈æod≈æiais <em>Lost myself at a Diddy party, didn‚Äôt know that‚Äôs how it go, I was in it for a new Ferrari, but it cost me way more than my soul, wasn‚Äôt worth all the fortune and fame</em> vis dƒólto tikriausiai yra sukurta dirbtinio intelekto.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F686d8a68-bbf6-4788-bd43-a780ade09921_1057x531.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F686d8a68-bbf6-4788-bd43-a780ade09921_1057x531.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:s